15template<typename S>
16ParameterVector<S>::ParameterVector(const int dim, const S values[]): VINIT(dim)
17{
18 assert(dim <= MaxDimension);
19 for (int i = 0; i < dim; ++i)
20 v[i] = values[i];
21 for (int i = dim; i < MaxDimension; ++i)
22 v[i] = S();
23}
